GitHubApiData.name: OpenFIRE-Boards-ESP32
GitHubApiData.description: Porting the shared board repository between the OpenFIRE firmware and the desktop app where the ESP32 boards were inserted

TranslatedDescriptions.ja: OpenFIREファームウェアとデスクトップアプリ間での共有ボードリポジトリの移植、ESP32ボードが挿入されている環境向け
TranslatedDescriptions.en: Porting the shared board repository between the OpenFIRE firmware and the desktop app where the ESP32 boards are used.
TranslatedDescriptions.fr: Portage du dépôt de la carte partagée entre le firmware OpenFIRE et l'application de bureau où les cartes ESP32 étaient insérées.
